    if (newValue == '') {
        g_form.clearValue('u_requester_phone');
        g_form.clearValue('u_requester_email');
		g_form.clearValue('submitter_s_org_code');
        return;
    }

    var usrID = g_form.getValue('u_requester');
    //g_form.addErrorMessage("Name ", usrID);
    var usrGA = new GlideAjax("DFASAJAXUtils");
    usrGA.addParam('sysparm_name', 'getUserInfo');
    usrGA.addParam('sysparm_usrID', usrID);
    usrGA.getXML(setUserInfo);

}

function setUserInfo(response) {
    var answer = response.responseXML.documentElement.getAttribute("answer");
    if (answer) {
        var usrInfo = JSON.parse(answer);
        g_form.setValue('u_requester_email', usrInfo.email);
        g_form.setValue('u_requester_phone', usrInfo.phone);
		g_form.setValue('submitter_s_org_code', usrInfo.department);
    }

}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>matthew .mcconkey</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-12-14 18:32:24</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>3af5df2f1b500d1068f92f82f54bcb85</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Populate Requester Info</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_3af5df2f1b500d1068f92f82f54bcb85</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>matthew .mcconkey</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-12-28 04:27:02</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onChange</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set display_value="u_harvest_user_information">58d8c25f2f5001107684b2e72799b6e9</variable_set><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>
